        <p class="hero-eyebrow">The Calm Focus Amino Acid</p>
        <p>L-theanine is an amino acid found in tea leaves, particularly green tea. It's the molecule behind tea's signature feel: calm focus, without the buzz of coffee or the drowsiness of relaxation.</p>
        <p>Today, L-theanine is one of the most studied amino acids for cognitive support. The research keeps coming back to alpha brain wave activity, the brain state associated with calm, focused attention.</p>
